	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>Friday&#44; 11th of Sivan &#40;May&#41;. 1859</date>.</p>
				<p>My dear friend&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Herewith I am sending to you my speech at <persName>Henry Moses&#39;</persName><lb/> funeral&#44; with the request to translate it at once and to have it printed.</p>
				<p><hi rend="underline">This time</hi> you must please me. I am counting on you.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Bravo for having openly expressed your opinion about<lb/> <persName>Jellinek</persName>. He himself <sic>wassnut</sic> out on <date>Passover</date> a year ago. But he must&#44;<lb/> he must.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Steinschneider</persName> shouts excitedly against <persName>Benjamin the II</persName>.<lb/> He calls him an ignorant man. Only free&#45;masonry supports him.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The filthiest that have ever appeared are the two eleven<lb/> ..... of the Judenzeitung&#44; 11&#44; 17 and 18. The attack on <persName>Frankel</persName> and against<lb/> <persName>Ullman</persName> in <placeName>Paris</placeName> is a terrible thing.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Again&#44; I repeat that it is a blameworthy thing to print<lb/> such things as that of <persName>Berend</persName>&#59; it is contrary to all law and justice. It<lb/> is not even old women&#39;s talk.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Please send me ten copies of the tenth&#44; eleventh&#44; and 20<lb/> of the last one.....</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Finally&#44; I send you hearty greetings.</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">Jonah Bondi</persName></p>
				<p>&#40;For <persName>Jellinek</persName>&#44; <persName>Benjamin II</persName> and <persName>Steinchneider</persName>&#44; see Jewish Encyclopedia.&#41;</p>
		</body>
